      <title>欧洲每桶100美元的汽油使燃烧的油更具吸引力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/gas-at-100-a-barrel-in-europe-makes-burning-oil-more-attractive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲高涨的天然气价格使燃烧石油用于工业用途更具成本效益，从而有可能提高该地区对桶的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/gas-at-100-a-barrel-in-europe-makes-burning-oil-more-attractive</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 13:26:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
