      <title>Saylor的策略在发布损失后恢复了比特币的购买</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/saylor-s-strategy-resumes-bitcoin-purchases-after-posting-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[策略是一家自称为比特币国库公司，直到最近才称为Microstrategy Inc.，他说，它在过去7天中收购了7.422亿美元的数字资产，恢复了10月下旬开始的每周购买。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/saylor-s-strategy-resumes-bitcoin-purchases-after-posting-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 13:10:14 GMT</pubDate>
